RC (Bayes Factor, BF=42.0) and in the opposite direction (BF=5.7). Our data suggest that Uganda may have been the cradle of Marburg virus in Africa.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Zehender, Gianguglielmo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sorrentino, Chiara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Veo, Carla", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fiaschi, Lisa", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gioffr\u00e8, Sonia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ebranati, Erika", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tanzi, Elisabetta", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ciccozzi, Massimo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lai, Alessia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Galli, Massimo", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Geographic dispersion", "Marburg virus", "Phylodynamics", "Ravn virus", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ce0d7fa60e823d994ad1d767d8b38281", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/38663c834b0aae7a2a87bf0c72f7a856111c1504ee2c153a9073d9a6a7a77d9f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/YDGPNTG9", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/YDGPNTG9", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/ca16cdfb5a08b3c4a54e44dcbb41579c!/b232119-234720", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "8-16", "title": "Infectio